{"pageProps":{"note":{"custom":{},"fname":"linux.setup-new-machine","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"d87ef268498f9afdee9946bd64ddff25","updated":1700214416964,"created":1700214416964,"id":"fhz8f7z30ezy00bz3pdet0j","desc":"","links":[],"anchors":{"set-up-a-new-machine":{"type":"header","text":"Set up a new machine","value":"set-up-a-new-machine","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"set-user-as-sudo":{"type":"header","text":"Set user as sudo","value":"set-user-as-sudo","line":9,"column":0,"depth":2},"awesome-wm":{"type":"header","text":"Awesome WM","value":"awesome-wm","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2},"zsh-setup":{"type":"header","text":"Zsh setup","value":"zsh-setup","line":45,"column":0,"depth":2},"fonts":{"type":"header","text":"Fonts","value":"fonts","line":56,"column":0,"depth":2},"hidpi-grub":{"type":"header","text":"HiDPI Grub","value":"hidpi-grub","line":61,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"6wjqcjgkrpeqtmzb1o8o1q8","data":{},"title":"Setup New Machine"},"body":"<h1 id=\"setup-new-machine\">Setup New Machine<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#setup-new-machine\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"set-up-a-new-machine\">Set up a new machine<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#set-up-a-new-machine\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"set-user-as-sudo\">Set user as sudo<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#set-user-as-sudo\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Switch to an another login account\n<ul>\n<li>ctrl + alt + &#x3C;F2/F12></li>\n<li>add user to the sudo group: <code>sudo add &#x3C;username> sudo</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"awesome-wm\">Awesome WM<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#awesome-wm\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Setup: <a href=\"https://wiki.debian.org/Awesome\">https://wiki.debian.org/Awesome</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>add <code>exec awesome</code> to your ~/.xinitrc</li>\n<li>find this <code>rc.lua</code> file in <code>/etc/xdg/awesome/</code>. Copy it to <code>~/.config/awesome/</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>High DPI</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/awesomewm/comments/inv3p8/how_to_set_scaleresolution_of_awesomewm/?rdt=59604\">https://www.reddit.com/r/awesomewm/comments/inv3p8/how_to_set_scaleresolution_of_awesomewm/?rdt=59604</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Set mouse scroll</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Update <code>/usr/share/X11/xorg.conf.d/40-libinput.conf</code>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<pre><code>  # Match on all types of devices but joysticks\n  Section \"InputClass\"\n          Identifier \"libinput pointer catchall\"\n          MatchIsPointer \"on\"\n          MatchDevicePath \"/dev/input/event*\"\n          Driver \"libinput\"\n          Option \"NaturalScrolling\" \"True\"\n  EndSection\n\n  ...\n\n  Section \"InputClass\"\n      Identifier \"libinput touchpad catchall\"\n      MatchIsTouchpad \"on\"\n      MatchDevicePath \"/dev/input/event*\"\n      Driver \"libinput\"\n      Option \"NaturalScrolling\" \"True\"\n  EndSection\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"zsh-setup\">Zsh setup<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#zsh-setup\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Install zsh: <code>sudo apt install zsh</code>\n<ul>\n<li>change shell: <code>chsh -s $(which zsh)</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Install oh-my-zsh: <a href=\"https://ohmyz.sh/#install\">https://ohmyz.sh/#install</a></li>\n<li>Link (hard link)\n<ul>\n<li>custom/themes/*</li>\n<li>.zshrc</li>\n<li>aliases.zsh</li>\n<li>my_command.zsh</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"fonts\">Fonts<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#fonts\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Ubuntu mono nerd fonts: <a href=\"https://www.nerdfonts.com/font-downloads\">https://www.nerdfonts.com/font-downloads</a></li>\n<li>Intel one mono: <a href=\"https://github.com/intel/intel-one-mono\">https://github.com/intel/intel-one-mono</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"hidpi-grub\">HiDPI Grub<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#hidpi-grub\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dedoimedo.com/computers/grub-hd-scaling-resolution.html\">https://www.dedoimedo.com/computers/grub-hd-scaling-resolution.html</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>update <code>/etc/default/grub</code>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<pre><code>  GRUB_GFXMODE=640x480\n  GRUB_GFXPAYLOAD=keep\n  GRUB_TERMINAL=gfxterm \n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>update the grub config: <code>sudo-update-grub</code></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron","value":"dendron","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["u5a2e2vvfn3x7k0shuvmb1b","qw8y69zxn8wr7tzz4gtcrrv","q7qw45jglqwmynary64q67c","6wjqcjgkrpeqtmzb1o8o1q8","3ervbn5we7t8v2l2vwtx847","4qi2z0z9fquupbd651xausx","sencgim78q74o1zuyvy1vz7","ue4oml1si982t3mmbthyxi9","zrogwjgtze8ne5joqpz8ty9","oesia0lbzh03fsoy124ck0k","el3p9zjue6h3b6zsl9oejkt","t5grkmcwvu4nl43igsj4gxz"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"# Welcome to my page\n\n- This is a place where I write my knowledge in both Vietnamese and English.\n- Please feel free to correct me if there is anything not right.\n\n## Contacts\n\n- [Github](https://github.com/thanhpp)\n- [Discord](https://discord.gg/ugNRjFNqjp)\n- [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/thanhpp/)\n\n## Dendron\n\n- [Home Page](https://wiki.dendron.so/)"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev